=============
Environment
=============
a) ubuntu 12.04 x64
b) jdk1.8.0_51

===================
1) without package
===================

tree java-native-interface-jni-tutorial/src
.
©¸©¤©¤ HelloWorld.java

a)  javac HelloWorld.java -> HelloWorld.class

b)  javah -jni HelloWord  -> HelloWorld.h

c)  implement HelloWord.c

/**
